{"tier":3,"question":"What is 'character displacement'?","answer":"When competing species evolve to become more different from each other in the same area","choices":["When a species changes its behavior in a new environment","When competing species evolve to become more different from each other in the same area","When animals migrate to avoid competition","When one species eliminates another"]},
